Security/cleanup pass

- Remove unused Dockerfile, .dockerignore, token.js (installer is
  native-only; token.js was superseded by `dashboard-link` and its docstring
  referenced the obsolete `docker compose exec` invocation).
- Parameterize Caddy auto-gen apex via PUBLIC_BASE_DOMAIN env var (was
  hardcoded to a personal domain). Empty default means generated configs
  contain only the service name and leak nothing.
- install-host.sh threads PUBLIC_BASE_DOMAIN through to the systemd unit and
  documents it in the override table.
- Fix stale "docker compose exec agent npm run link" doc comments in
  link.js / tunnel.js to point at the native `dashboard-link` wrapper.
- Drop "token" entry from package.json scripts.
